HEADWORD: nigger
<hw>nig"ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A negro; -- in vulgar
derision or depreciation. It is usually intended and interpreted as
highly insulting and vulgar.</def> <mark>[Low, deprecatory, and
vulgar]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

